import UseFiltersToggle from './UseFiltersToggle'

export class SidePannel extends Component {
    render() {
         return (
           <Col sm={2}>
             <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="first">
  <Row>
    <Col sm={9}>
      <Nav variant="primary" className="flex-column">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link eventKey="first">
            My Researches
            <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="first">
  <Row>
    <Col sm={3}>
      <Nav variant="primary" className="flex-column">

      </Nav>
    </Col>
    <Col sm={9}>
      <Tab.Content>
        <Tab.Pane eventKey="first">
          <Sonnet />
        </Tab.Pane>
        <Tab.Pane eventKey="second">
          <Sonnet />
        </Tab.Pane>
      </Tab.Content>
    </Col>
  </Row>
</Tab.Container>
            </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link eventKey="second">Tab 2</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
    </Col>
    
  </Row>
</Tab.Container>
           </Col>

        )
    }
}

export default SidePannel
